layout.p:
Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 26;
                                                  written lines: 26; Uniform layout. Two columns of 26 written lines. The last four books begin in the middle of a column, after a blank space of four lines. A new pericope is either headed by the word 'parashah' or indicated by the same word in the margin. Thick parchment ruled with hard-point on the hair-side of a folio. Pricking hardly visible.
